title: weeklyhours.2.apk
description: Do you have the kind of job where you're required to calculate your own hours? Well now you can easily with this App! Add your start and finish times and your hourly rate. Set automatic deduction for lunch, perhaps it's a half hour for example. See your total for the week before taxes are taken out. Has an e-mail option, you could e-mail your boss directly. Enjoy and re-seed please!
